    <item>
      <title>对俄罗斯边境地区的袭击让人们认识到普京战争的代价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/attacks-near-russia-s-ukraine-border-bring-home-costs-of-putin-s-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对与乌克兰接壤的俄罗斯地区的致命袭击越来越让人认识到弗拉基米尔·普京入侵的代价。这并不意味着人们会因战争而攻击俄罗斯总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/attacks-near-russia-s-ukraine-border-bring-home-costs-of-putin-s-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 16:00:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普公开暗示支持 15 周堕胎禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/trump-publicly-hints-at-support-for-15-week-abortion-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在接受电台采访时表示，他将支持为期 15 周的堕胎禁令，但有例外，这是他首次就阻碍共和党的问题公开提供具体细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/trump-publicly-hints-at-support-for-15-week-abortion-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 16:00:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑山坚持将道权交给韩国，冷落美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/montenegro-sticks-to-handing-do-kwon-to-korea-in-a-snub-to-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黑山上诉法院确认了一项裁决，即韩国对名誉扫地的加密货币大亨 Do Kwon 的引渡要求优先于美国的类似要求，美国检察官也希望因 2022 年 TerraUSD 稳定币价值 400 亿美元的崩溃而对他进行审判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/montenegro-sticks-to-handing-do-kwon-to-korea-in-a-snub-to-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:56:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>议长约翰逊吹捧共和党在资助协议中移民拘留问题上获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/speaker-touts-gop-wins-on-migrant-detention-in-funding-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，众议院议长迈克·约翰逊 (Mike Johnson) 周三提倡增加对移民拘留的资助，并削减多样性和气候项目，试图在共和党会议上推销 1 万亿美元的支出协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/speaker-touts-gop-wins-on-migrant-detention-in-funding-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 14:44:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
